  "texts": [
    "Specifically, CodeS-15B is based on StarCoder-15B, while CodeS-(1B, 3B, 7B) are derived from the respective StarCoderBase-(1B, 3B, 7B).",
    "Then we optimize the language modeling objective that is widely used in prior pre-trained language models like GPT [52] and LLaMA [64].",
    "Specifically, given a sequence 𝑥 consisting of 𝑛 tokens, denoted as 𝑡 0, 𝑡 1, 𝑡 2,..., 𝑡 𝑛-1, our objective is to maximize the likelihood of the entire sequence.",
    "This is achieved by calculating the product of the conditional probabilities for each token:𝑝 (𝑥) = 𝑛-1 𝑖=1 𝑝 (𝑡 𝑖 |𝑡 1, 𝑡 2,...𝑡 𝑖 -1).",
    "(2)To optimize the objective, we employ the AdamW optimizer [44] with parameters set to 𝛽 1 = 0.9, 𝛽 2 = 0.95, and 𝜖 = 10 -8."
  ],
